   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Airline Pilots Craft Ads to Improve Image
   ----
   By Asra Q. Nomani
</HL>
<DATE>
08/22/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B2
</SO>
<CO>
   LABOR SQD OMC AXP
</CO>
